title: Competitive OCE Gaming Discord
body:
[Competitive OCE Gaming Discord](https://discord.gg/Y93kJJN) which is currently growing and on the rise. Looking for all members, beginners to veterans. If you lack people to play with and are looking to play enjoyable league games with voice communication then this discord is for you!

For more info on features or wish to become a moderator, connect to the discord and contact staff.
